        <h3>Permissions</h3>
        <p>When an account is created for each new user a permission is also granted (either, Read, Change or Admin). After the user logs ini in he can see what the system has defined as his permission by looking at the user information banner displayed accross the top of each page. "Change" permission is granted based on the user's need and proffeciency in using the database. These are some of the measures taken to protect the integrity of the information you put into the database.</p>
